sequenceDiagram
    autonumber off

    participant XS as XML Source
    participant FA as Function App
    participant ZB as Zerobus
    participant DI as Delta Ingest
    participant DB as DLT Bronze
    participant DS as DLT Silver
    participant DG as DLT Gold
    participant SB as Service Bus
    participant EH as Event Hub
    participant SP as Spark Streaming
    participant LB as Lakebase
    participant AP as API

    rect rgb(210, 228, 255)
        Note over XS,AP: Approach 1 — Function App + Zerobus + DLT

        XS->>FA: XML payload
        FA->>FA: Parse XML → JSON (~0.5s)
        FA->>ZB: JSON record via gRPC
        ZB->>DI: Write to Delta table (~1.4s ACK)
        DI->>DB: Auto Loader pickup (~2s)
        DB->>DS: Enrich, H3 index, validate (~2s)
        DS->>DG: MERGE + aggregate (~2s)
        DG->>LB: Unity Catalog sync
        AP->>LB: SELECT query (<0.1s)
        Note over XS,AP: Total latency: ~8–12 seconds end-to-end
    end

    rect rgb(210, 245, 220)
        Note over XS,AP: Approach 2 — Event Hub Direct (Recommended)

        XS->>SB: XML payload
        SB->>EH: Native forward
        EH->>SP: Kafka-compatible read (~0.5s)
        SP->>SP: Parse XML + enrich + H3 + MERGE (~2–3s)
        SP->>LB: Write gold tables (Unity Catalog sync)
        AP->>LB: SELECT query (<0.1s)
        Note over XS,AP: Total latency: ~3–5 seconds end-to-end
    end
